<div class="question-card" id="card-109" data-qid="109" data-type="multi" data-choose="3">
  <div class="card-header">
    <span class="q-number">Q 110</span>
    <span class="q-tag multi">Choose 3</span>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="question-text">
      A network administrator is designing the layout of a new wireless network. Which three areas of concern should be accounted for when building a wireless network? (Choose three.)
    </p>
    <div class="options" id="opts-109">
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="0">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">A</span>
        <span class="opt-text">mobility options</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="1">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">B</span>
        <span class="opt-text">security</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="2">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">C</span>
        <span class="opt-text">interference</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="3">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">D</span>
        <span class="opt-text">coverage area</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="4">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">E</span>
        <span class="opt-text">packet collision</span>
      </button>
      <button class="option-btn multi" data-idx="5">
        <span class="opt-indicator"></span>
        <span class="opt-letter">F</span>
        <span class="opt-text">extensive cabling</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="submit-wrap" style="display: none;">
      <button class="submit-btn multi-pending" id="submit-109" disabled>Submit Answer</button>
      <span class="pending-count" id="pendingCount-109">0 / 3 selected</span>
    </div>

    <div class="explanation" id="exp-109">
      <div class="exp-header">
        <span class="exp-verdict" id="verdict-109"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-body">
        The three areas of concern for wireless networks focus on the size of the coverage area, any nearby interference, and providing network security. Extensive cabling is not a concern for wireless networks, as a wireless network will require minimal cabling for providing wireless access to hosts. Mobility options are not a component of the areas of concern for wireless networks.
      </div>
    </div>
